 <H1>Validating Adaptation</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Idea: Exploit additional hardware (unused gates) for additional redundancy and validation
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Increases system reliability without major resource cost
<LI>High Level generation of Validation circuits; invariants, complements, etc. (automatic and manual)
<LI>Wide range of redundancy possible, validation can be partial to multiple in time and versions
<LI>Can detect and signal errors or failures
<LI>
<LI>=&#062 May be the only approach possible for dynamic adaptation</UL></UL></P>
